OL,3,CFormer footballer Clarke Carlisle
OL,4,Ctalks mental health and wellbeing
OL,6,FClarke Carlisle joined Gamal
OL,7,FFarnbulleh in the Granada Reports
OL,8,Fstudio to talk about his work around
OL,9,Fmental health.
OL,11,FFormer Preston and Burnley footballer
OL,12,FClarke Carlisle says he works on his
OL,13,Fmental health every day since he
OL,14,Fattempted to take his own life.
OL,16,FIt has been a decade since Clarke
OL,17,Fstood in front of a lorry after
OL,18,Fstruggling with depression and an
OL,19,Faddiction to alcohol and gambling.
