OL,3,CFormer footballer Clarke Carlisle
OL,4,Ctalks mental health and wellbeing
OL,6,FHe started his own charity, The Clarke
OL,7,FCarlisle Foundation for Dual
OL,8,FDiagnosis, to help others in similar
OL,9,Fsituations.
OL,11,FClarke said: "When I talk about 2014,
OL,12,Fit's almost like talking about a
OL,13,Fdifferent person let alone a different
OL,14,Flifetime.
OL,16,F"And when you are sat on the edge of
OL,17,Fthe precipice and your thoughts and
OL,18,Femotions are all consuming, never mind
OL,19,Foverwhelming, it can feel like a very
OL,20,Flonely place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
