OL,3,CFormer footballer Clarke Carlisle
OL,4,Ctalks mental health and wellbeing
OL,6,F"But with the right help and with the
OL,7,Fright approach to that help, this type
OL,8,Fof
OL,10,Fwellness that I feel today is
OL,11,Favailable for all."
OL,13,FClarke says having an "appetite" and
OL,14,F"an open mind to be able to try
OL,15,Fsomething new" are just some of the
OL,16,Ftools needed to aid others who are
OL,17,Fwanting to begin their mental health
OL,18,Fand wellbeing journey.
