OL,4,Ctalks mental health and wellbeing
OL,6,FClarke said creating or having a safe
OL,7,Fenvironment to speak about mental
OL,8,Fhealth is needed in order for people
OL,9,Fto feel comfortable to open up.
OL,11,F"You need a space where you know
OL,12,Fyou're not going to be judged and
OL,13,Fequally it's creating a safe space
OL,14,Fwhere you can share things with people
OL,15,Fand they have empathy with you."
OL,17,F"It is quite incredible when I think
OL,18,Fback to 10 years ago, it's it's like
OL,19,Fthinking about different human being.
