OL,3,CFormer footballer Clarke Carlisle
OL,4,Ctalks mental health and wellbeing
OL,6,F"With how far I have come, I can sit
OL,7,Fback and reflect and I can actually
OL,8,Ffeel some pride about the progression
OL,9,Fthat I've made and I feel pride
OL,10,Fbecause I know that I sit here today
OL,11,Fauthentically me.
OL,13,F"I will share who I am with you and
OL,14,FI'm no longer overly concerned whether
OL,15,Fyou like me or not, that's your
OL,16,Fprerogative, but that's not where my
OL,17,Fsteam of my identity."
